Map Einstein Knowledge Creation Responses to Knowledge Fields

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED:
Customize Application AND Knowledge User.
To map fields, select Edit, Add Field, choose a Knowledge field and map it to a response. To remove fields, click Delete.

IMPORTANT: When mapping fields, all fields across Knowledge record types are available if accessible. If the user generating an article doesn't have access to a field, it won't be populated.

To improve Einstein's responses with knowledge base and case information, set up Service AI Grounding for cases.
